{"tid":2141303,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"傳談判有進展 古天奴將入「廠」","createTime":"2020-08-05T14:23:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-05T14:57:57.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"fd93621025eb83a442d216b25bad9b4195eca593","tid":2141303,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T14:23:06.000Z","msg":"【Now Sports】古天奴即將找到新東家，以借將身份回歸英超加盟阿仙奴。<br />\n<br />\n西班牙《Sport》報道，阿仙奴極度鍾情於今季被借到拜仁慕尼黑的攻中古天奴（Philippe Coutinho），而且跟巴塞隆拿的談判已經進入另一階段，很大機會成功借用這名巴西國腳。<br />\n<br />\n經理人祖拉捷恩旗下的中堅大衛路爾斯、右閘蘇亞利斯都正效力阿仙奴，令古天奴來投的成數大增。兵工廠同時青睞祖拉捷恩另一名客戶韋利安，願意提供3年合約，以免費簽入這名拒絕續約車路士的31歲翼鋒。<br />\n<br />\n雖然巴塞仍然未能賣走古天奴，但在新型冠狀病毒疫情下能夠收回借用費及節省人工，已經算不錯。另外，據知巴塞希望賣走前鋒比夫韋治、中堅杜迪保，兩人皆有望轉戰英超。"},{"pid":"72be046a89b2572f06485d7e63b069c2d03520af","tid":2141303,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T14:23:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pa1.narvii.com/7111/e49766ee5e3eb5f11a06c83fa052d3f573522703r1-480-270_hq.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpa1.narvii.com%2F7111%2Fe49766ee5e3eb5f11a06c83fa052d3f573522703r1-480-270_hq.gif&h=4c85dc27&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3b762bb5d764606f23c13a1095eb243e0e151590","tid":2141303,"uid":87155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T14:33:27.000Z","msg":"屌咩 唔好呀"},{"pid":"d722d768080f125df484f1c041efcb75f715fbd6","tid":2141303,"uid":186431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T14:39:32.000Z","msg":"又吹<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"923005306b0b03ced798dc77961d6c15558726a8","tid":2141303,"uid":209773,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3b762bb5d764606f23c13a1095eb243e0e151590","tid":2141303,"uid":87155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T14:33:27.000Z","msg":"屌咩 唔好呀"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T14:39:43.000Z","msg":"好失禮你？"},{"pid":"6f3c5d06fce485fd12002f4d72686ce960197ece","tid":2141303,"uid":87155,"like"